{
  "stem": "27507.11",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we walked-- we spent some days in Praga, and then we walked across some 10 kilometers to [INAUDIBLE] to a little place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we moved from-- and that was still all a front line.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was artillery there everywhere and shooting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we went to the further away from Warsaw, and my father decided that he wants to go to Lublin where the first Polish government, the communist government, was.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, somehow, in one way or another by walking and by horse cart and so on went to Lublin, and finally got to Lublin probably at the end of September.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my father found that there was this Polish-- first Polish government, which was practically all Poles who were in Russia and the Soviet Union during the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so that was a communist government.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father, since he was a lawyer and he found some people who knew in there, in the Department of Justice in this government, he found-- they offered him a job.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a lawyer, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, working for the ministry, for the justice ministry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he worked in Lublin in the next few months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since we worked for the government, we got as well a room in an official apartment block belonging to the government, so we had a place to live.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly life became relatively normal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to school and we had enough to eat, and we had-- and we had a room to live and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, my mother was not there, and we didn't know what happened to my mother because she was on the other side of the Vistula and she was caught up in the uprising and could never then cross to the other side of the Vistula.",
      "word_count": 46
    }
  ],
